    },
    {
      "sourcePath": "D:\\workspace\\CodeBuddyWorkSpace\\RebornG_codebuddy\\doc\\original work\\reverend-insanity.txt",
      "chapterId": "ch_2295",
      "paragraphId": "ch_2295_p0075",
      "startOffset": 8006784,
      "endOffset": 8006787,
      "summary": "与魏无伤同时期升仙的蛊师"
    },
    {
      "sourcePath": "D:\\workspace\\CodeBuddyWorkSpace\\RebornG_codebuddy\\doc\\original work\\reverend-insanity.txt",
      "chapterId": "ch_2295",
      "paragraphId": "ch_2295_p0060",
      "startOffset": 8006251,
      "endOffset": 8006292,
      "summary": "翼家帮助莫利升仙，莫利是盗天真传，翼家受盗天魔尊恩惠"
    },
    {
      "sourcePath": "D:\\workspace\\CodeBuddyWorkSpace\\RebornG_codebuddy\\doc\\original work\\reverend-insanity.txt",
      "chapterId": "ch_2295",
      "paragraphId": "ch_2295_p0068",
      "startOffset": 8006607,
      "endOffset": 8006617,
      "summary": "周一口称莫利为自己人，因盗天魔尊的恩惠而相助"
    },
    {
      "sourcePath": "D:\\workspace\\CodeBuddyWorkSpace\\RebornG_codebuddy\\doc\\original work\\reverend-insanity.txt",
      "chapterId": "ch_2295",
      "paragraphId": "ch_2295_p0074",
      "startOffset": 8006748,
      "endOffset": 8006758,
      "summary": "魏无伤的本命蛊是贼人蛊，试图升炼为仙蛊但失败"
    },
    {
      "sourcePath": "D:\\workspace\\CodeBuddyWorkSpace\\RebornG_codebuddy\\doc\\original work\\reverend-insanity.txt",
      "chapterId": "ch_2295",
      "paragraphId": "ch_2295_p0014",
      "startOffset": 8004271,
      "endOffset": 8004282,
      "summary": "孔日天碎窍渡劫，经历三天飞轮劫，成为六转蛊仙，得到上等福地"
    },
    {
      "sourcePath": "D:\\workspace\\CodeBuddyWorkSpace\\RebornG_codebuddy\\doc\\original work\\reverend-insanity.txt",
      "chapterId": "ch_2295",
      "paragraphId": "ch_2295_p0039",
      "startOffset": 8005252,
      "endOffset": 8005303,
      "summary": "孔日天升仙成为蛊仙，但天地二气残余不足，本命蛊未能升为仙蛊"
    },
    {
      "sourcePath": "D:\\workspace\\CodeBuddyWorkSpace\\RebornG_codebuddy\\doc\\original work\\reverend-insanity.txt",
      "chapterId": "ch_2295",
      "paragraphId": "ch_2295_p0056",
      "startOffset": 8006168,
      "endOffset": 8006200,
      "summary": "孔日天计划在宝黄天与方源意志交易炼制仙蛊"
    },
    {
      "sourcePath": "D:\\workspace\\CodeBuddyWorkSpace\\RebornG_codebuddy\\doc\\original work\\reverend-insanity.txt",
      "chapterId": "ch_2295",
      "paragraphId": "ch_2295_p0072",
      "startOffset": 8006688,
      "endOffset": 8006698,
      "summary": "魏无伤渡劫成功，成为人道蛊仙，获得上等福地，但升炼本命仙蛊失败"
    },
    {
      "sourcePath": "D:\\workspace\\CodeBuddyWorkSpace\\RebornG_codebuddy\\doc\\original work\\reverend-insanity.txt",
      "chapterId": "ch_2295",
      "paragraphId": "ch_2295_p0076",
      "startOffset": 8006818,
      "endOffset": 8006828,
      "summary": "魏无伤在深夜沉眠时灵感勃发，开悟出贼人蛊的仙蛊方，但实际是被衍化仙阵改变了记忆"
    },
    {
      "sourcePath": "D:\\workspace\\CodeBuddyWorkSpace\\RebornG_codebuddy\\doc\\original work\\reverend-insanity.txt",
      "chapterId": "ch_2295",
      "paragraphId": "ch_2295_p0086",
      "startOffset": 8007120,
      "endOffset": 8007130,
      "summary": "魏无伤炼蛊失败后，怀疑是因为仙蛊唯一性，但认为不可能，因为贼人仙蛊是他开创的"
    }
  ],
